<i> MY SMILE IS STUCK.</i>

45:14.162 --> 45:16.462
<i> STUCK. STUCK. STUCK. STUCK.</i>

45:16.464 --> 45:19.698
<i> STUCK. STUCK. STUCK. STUCK.</i>

