PLEASE. PLEASE FIT IN.

46:03.835 --> 46:06.002
HE CAN'T GET IN HERE,
CAN HE?

46:08.372 --> 46:10.339
HOLD FAST,
RIGHT, DAD?

46:19.047 --> 46:20.313
HE'S TOO STRONG!

46:23.050 --> 46:25.049
WE NEED SOMETHING
TO BRACE THE DOOR!

46:27.419 --> 46:28.952
SOMETHING TOUGH.

46:28.954 --> 46:31.287
GO! GO!

46:43.232 --> 46:44.332
MOM,
YOU CAN'T GO UP THERE!

46:44.334 --> 46:45.499
JUST TELL DAD TO HURRY!

46:45.501 --> 46:47.000
DAD! HURRY!

46:47.002 --> 46:48.134
I<i> AM</i> HURRYING!

46:59.112 --> 47:00.244
UNH!

47:00.246 --> 47:02.045
MOM, ARE YOU OKAY?!

47:02.047 --> 47:04.414
I'M OKAY!
JUST STAY DOWN THERE!

47:04.416 --> 47:05.515
DAD, HURRY!

47:05.517 --> 47:07.316
GOD!

47:13.522 --> 47:14.955
RAY!

47:22.797 --> 47:25.230
HE'S ALMOST THROUGH!

47:25.232 --> 47:27.999
HOLD ON!

47:28.001 --> 47:29.000
DAD!

47:29.002 --> 47:30.468
WATCH OUT!

47:31.504 --> 47:32.936
RAY,
GIVE ME THE PIPE!

47:32.938 --> 47:34.370
WEDGE IT
UNDER THE HANDLE!

47:34.372 --> 47:35.804
WATCH OUT, MOM!

47:53.986 --> 47:55.051
WATCH OUT, CLAIRE!

47:56.354 --> 47:58.187
DIE!

48:01.525 --> 48:03.458
RAY!

48:03.460 --> 48:05.226
RAY!

48:06.896 --> 48:08.395
RAY!

48:09.431 --> 48:10.463
RAY!

