RAY! RAY!
HE'S NOT GETTING IN!

48:17.204 --> 48:19.003
HE'S NOT GETTING IN!

48:19.005 --> 48:20.270
IT'LL HOLD!

48:22.974 --> 48:24.340
IT WILL.

48:24.342 --> 48:25.341
OKAY?

48:26.410 --> 48:27.409
OKAY.

48:28.578 --> 48:29.944
HEY.

48:31.947 --> 48:33.881
HEY.

48:44.391 --> 48:46.258
HOLD FAST?

48:48.594 --> 48:50.494
HOLD FAST.

49:30.064 --> 49:32.298
HE'S STILL UP THERE.

49:32.300 --> 49:34.533
WHY ISN'T HE LEAVING?

49:34.535 --> 49:38.069
WHY WON'T HE JUST
GO AWAY?

49:38.071 --> 49:39.904
I DON'T KNOW.

49:44.275 --> 49:47.277
HE'S UP TO SOMETHING.

49:47.279 --> 49:50.580
What could he be up to?

49:50.582 --> 49:53.382
Why is he still
standing there?

50:30.416 --> 50:32.315
<i> THAT'S</i> WHAT HE'S DOING.

50:33.684 --> 50:35.184
HE'S WAITING.

50:35.186 --> 50:38.187
WAITING FOR WHAT?

50:38.189 --> 50:39.955
THE REST OF THEM.

51:22.529 --> 51:24.096
HEY, LOOK, ZOE,
THERE IT IS.

51:24.098 --> 51:26.431
THE WATER TOWER OVER THERE --
YOU SEE IT?

51:28.500 --> 51:30.334
SO ONCE WE'RE PAST THAT,
WE'RE OUT OF KINGSVILLE.

51:30.336 --> 51:33.170
THEN WE'LL BE SAFE?
SAFE FROM THE SICK PEOPLE?

51:33.172 --> 51:35.572
THAT'S RIGHT, SWEETIE.
SAFE FROM THE SICK PEOPLE.

51:53.621 --> 51:55.153
WHY ARE ALL THOSE PEOPLE
HEADED BACK?

51:55.155 --> 51:57.021
I DON'T KNOW.

51:58.223 --> 52:00.257
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
WE COULDN'T STAY,

52:00.259 --> 52:02.158
THAT IT WAS DANGEROUS.

52:02.160 --> 52:03.559
MAYBE
EVERYTHING'S OKAY NOW.

52:03.561 --> 52:05.193
YOU THINK THAT'S POSSIBLE?

52:05.195 --> 52:06.427
I DON'T KNOW.

52:09.564 --> 52:11.497
GOT TO BE ABLE
TO GET SOMETHING HERE.

52:11.499 --> 52:13.098
MAYBE A.M.?

52:15.435 --> 52:16.600
RAY, WATCH OUT!

52:21.739 --> 52:24.673
LET US OUT!
THERE'S NOWHERE ELSE TO GO!

52:27.377 --> 52:28.777
<i> ALL CIVILIANS IN KINGSVILLE</i>

52:28.779 --> 52:30.345
<i> MUST RETURN TO THEIR HOMES</i>
<i> AT ONCE</i>

52:30.347 --> 52:33.448
<i> UNTIL THE CDC</i>
<i> STABILIZES THE OUTBREAK.</i>

