<i> THIS IS A QUARANTINE ORDER</i>
<i> SIGNED BY GOVERNOR SCHROEDER</i>

52:35.819 --> 52:37.552
<i> UNDER EMERGENCY CODE 11.</i>

52:37.554 --> 52:39.420
<i> THIS IS FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY.</i>

52:39.422 --> 52:41.855
<i> REPEAT --</i>
<i> ALL CIVILIANS IN KINGSVILLE</i>

52:41.857 --> 52:43.489
<i> MUST RETURN TO THEIR HOMES</i>
<i> AT ONCE</i>

52:43.491 --> 52:45.791
<i> UNTIL THE CDC</i>
<i> STABILIZES THE OUTBREAK.</i>

