52:50.563 --> 52:51.862
<i> THIS IS FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY.</i>

52:53.232 --> 52:54.531
<i> ALL CIVILIANS IN KINGSVILLE</i>

52:54.533 --> 52:56.332
<i> MUST RETURN TO THEIR HOMES</i>
<i> AT ONCE</i>

52:56.334 --> 52:57.666
<i> UNTIL THE CDC</i>
<i> STABILIZES THE OUTBREAK.</i>

52:57.668 --> 53:00.201
MOM,
WHAT'S A "CORE AND TINE"?

53:01.169 --> 53:03.403
QUARANTINE.

53:03.405 --> 53:05.772
IT MEANS
THEY'RE NOT LETTING US OUT.

53:05.774 --> 53:07.540
YOU MEAN
WE'RE TRAPPED IN HERE?

53:07.542 --> 53:09.708
<i> THE CDC IS WORKING CLOSELY</i>
<i> WITH THE NATIONAL GUARD</i>

53:09.710 --> 53:10.842
<i> TO SUPPORT THE DEPLOYMENT...</i>

53:13.778 --> 53:15.345
<i> YOU WILL RECEIVE</i>
<i> FURTHER NOTIFICATION</i>

53:15.347 --> 53:16.679
<i> OF THE RESPONSE TEAMS...</i>

53:21.950 --> 53:23.684
GET BACK!

53:49.573 --> 53:53.275
MOM. DAD.

53:53.277 --> 53:54.542
THEY'RE HERE.

54:27.708 --> 54:29.741
DARLENE'S NOT GONNA HOLD!

54:29.743 --> 54:31.809
WE NEED SOMETHING ELSE!

54:31.811 --> 54:33.410
GO!

54:44.555 --> 54:46.655
RUN!

54:51.027 --> 54:53.627
GET ZOE
TO THE BEDROOM! GO!
HOLD ON!

54:58.731 --> 55:01.299
THAT'S NOT GONNA
LAST LONG.

55:01.301 --> 55:03.501
RAY, HELP ME!

55:13.877 --> 55:16.011
HOW LONG
IS THAT GONNA LAST?!
COUPLE OF MINUTES.

55:16.013 --> 55:17.012
WE'VE GOT TO
GET OUT OF HERE!

55:17.014 --> 55:18.446
THEY'RE BLOCKING
THE DOOR!

55:18.448 --> 55:19.613
MOM, DAD.

55:19.615 --> 55:21.481
THE DOOR'S
NOT THE ONLY WAY OUT.

55:25.619 --> 55:27.353
THE PERISCOPE!

55:31.057 --> 55:32.957
I THINK WE CAN FIT.
I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT YOU, RAY.

55:32.959 --> 55:34.892
I'LL BE FINE.
JUST --

55:34.894 --> 55:37.294
HURRY.

56:03.317 --> 56:04.583
DAD!
CLAIRE!

56:04.585 --> 56:06.484
OKAY, RAY. IT'S CLEAR.
GET ZoZo.

56:06.486 --> 56:08.853
YOU READY?
GET ZoZo!

56:08.855 --> 56:10.454
COME ON.

56:10.456 --> 56:11.555
Ray, now!

56:11.557 --> 56:12.622
HERE,
WATCH YOUR HEAD.

56:12.624 --> 56:14.457
TAKE YOUR MOM'S HAND!
NO!

56:16.394 --> 56:17.659
YOU GOT HER?
GOT HER!

56:25.733 --> 56:26.798
OKAY, RAY, SHE'S UP.
COME ON.

56:34.073 --> 56:35.906
I CAN'T FIT.

56:44.681 --> 56:46.014
I CAN'T FIT.

56:46.016 --> 56:48.483
OH, COME ON!

56:50.119 --> 56:51.852
CLAIRE, GRAB MY WRIST!

56:51.854 --> 56:53.386
WHAT?
GRAB IT!

56:53.388 --> 56:55.388
HOLD TIGHT.

56:58.959 --> 57:00.725
OH, GOD!
DAD!

57:02.428 --> 57:03.493
DAD! DAD!

57:03.495 --> 57:05.394
AAH! GOD!

57:05.396 --> 57:06.395
ARE YOU OKAY?!

57:06.397 --> 57:08.930
I'M O--

57:08.932 --> 57:10.831
I'M OKAY.

57:31.884 --> 57:33.084
NO, DADDY! COME ON!

57:33.086 --> 57:34.785
RAY!

57:34.787 --> 57:36.820
REMEMBER OUR PROMISE.

57:36.822 --> 57:38.121
ZOE COMES FIRST.

57:42.527 --> 57:43.759
AAH!

57:48.732 --> 57:50.865
COME ON.

57:50.867 --> 57:53.067
COME ON!

57:53.069 --> 57:54.835
NO! RAY!

57:54.837 --> 57:56.770
NO, DADDY!
OH, RAY!

57:56.772 --> 57:58.037
OH, GOD, HELP!

57:59.673 --> 58:01.539
DADDY! DADDY!

58:03.075 --> 58:04.707
OHH! GOD!

58:06.576 --> 58:07.809
DADDY!

58:07.811 --> 58:09.844
NO! NO! DAD! LET ME GO!

58:09.846 --> 58:11.579
WE CAN HELP HIM!

58:11.581 --> 58:13.547
I PROMISED HIM
THAT I WOULD PROTECT YOU!
NO! NO!

58:13.549 --> 58:15.682
I PROMISED HIM
THAT I WOULD PROTECT YOU!
I DON'T CARE!

58:15.684 --> 58:16.683
I PROMISED HIM!

58:16.685 --> 58:17.717
I HATE YOU!

58:17.719 --> 58:19.752
I HATE YOU!

58:19.754 --> 58:22.721
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.
I JUST -- I JUST --
LET ME GO.

58:22.723 --> 58:24.522
IT'S OKAY.

58:32.863 --> 58:34.563
WE HAVE TO RUN.

58:35.731 --> 58:36.831
RUN!

58:46.574 --> 58:47.573
OLIVE! OLIVE!

58:47.575 --> 58:48.707
ZoZo! COME BACK!

58:51.144 --> 58:54.678
RUN!

59:10.692 --> 59:11.992
ARE YOU OKAY, HONEY?

59:11.994 --> 59:13.994
YEAH, I'M OKAY.

59:13.996 --> 59:14.995
COME ON.

59:14.997 --> 59:16.563
COME ON.

59:24.771 --> 59:27.005
WHERE -- WHERE ARE WE?

59:28.207 --> 59:31.242
WHERE IT ALL STARTED.

59:46.922 --> 59:48.689
WHAT DO WE DO?!

59:48.691 --> 59:50.590
RUN! KEEP RUNNING!

1:00:05.870 --> 1:00:07.871
THE BREATHERS!
THEY'RE COMING!

1:00:18.581 --> 1:00:20.382
SHE DREAMED
THEY FOUND US.

1:00:24.153 --> 1:00:25.887
THEY'RE STILL
LOOKING FOR US.

1:00:31.759 --> 1:00:33.159
THEY HATE US A LOT,
DON'T THEY?

1:00:33.161 --> 1:00:35.060
TO KEEP HUNTING US
LIKE THAT.

1:00:35.062 --> 1:00:36.961
THEY'VE ALWAYS
TRAVELED IN GROUPS BEFORE.

1:00:36.963 --> 1:00:38.295
YEAH, WELL,
I CAN FIGHT THEM.

1:00:38.297 --> 1:00:39.696
THAT'S SUICIDE,
AND YOU KNOW IT.

1:00:39.698 --> 1:00:40.897
WHAT'S
A "CORE AND TINE"?

1:00:40.899 --> 1:00:42.031
IT MEANS
THEY'RE NOT LETTING US OUT.

1:00:42.033 --> 1:00:44.299
The Breathers.

1:01:17.098 --> 1:01:18.864
LET US GO!

1:01:19.900 --> 1:01:20.932
LET US GO!

1:01:23.803 --> 1:01:25.769
LET US GO!
LET US OUT!

1:01:25.771 --> 1:01:27.203
NO!

1:01:49.322 --> 1:01:53.057
MOM,
IT'S AN EARTHQUAKE.

1:01:53.059 --> 1:01:56.226
NO, SWEETIE,
IT CAN'T BE.

1:01:56.228 --> 1:01:58.695
KINGSVILLE
DOESN'T HAVE EARTHQUAKES.

1:02:10.041 --> 1:02:12.775
WHY THE HELL
DOES THE CDC NEED MILITARY JETS?

1:02:12.777 --> 1:02:14.276
THEY'RE TURNING AROUND.

1:02:27.088 --> 1:02:30.790
THEY JUST TOLD EVERYONE
TO GO BACK INTO TOWN.

1:02:32.093 --> 1:02:33.926
MOM, DAD,
THEY'RE COMING!

1:02:37.197 --> 1:02:39.263
COME ON!
WE GOT TO GET OUT OF HERE!

1:02:39.265 --> 1:02:40.497
COME ON,
COME ON, COME ON!

1:02:40.499 --> 1:02:41.931
NO, NO, NO!
TOO FAR TO WALK THERE!

1:02:48.470 --> 1:02:50.804
KINGSVILLE ELEMENTARY!
WHAT?!

1:02:50.806 --> 1:02:52.338
THERE'S A FALLOUT SHELTER
OUT BACK!

1:02:52.340 --> 1:02:53.739
BUT I DON'T KNOW
IF IT'S SAFE.

1:02:53.741 --> 1:02:55.507
WELL, IT'S SAFER THAN HERE.
COME ON.

1:02:55.509 --> 1:02:57.174
COME ON!

1:03:07.349 --> 1:03:09.483
GOT TO GO, GUYS.
GO.

1:03:21.894 --> 1:03:23.261
WHERE IS IT?
THERE!

1:03:23.263 --> 1:03:24.495
WHERE'S THE DOOR?!
THERE!

1:03:33.803 --> 1:03:36.437
- THEY'RE COMING! HURRY!
- RAY, HURRY!

1:03:40.941 --> 1:03:42.841
LET'S GO. COME ON.
I GOT YOU.

1:03:42.843 --> 1:03:45.043
ALL RIGHT, COME ON!
COME ON!

1:03:47.881 --> 1:03:49.513
CLAIRE! SHUT IT NOW!

1:04:04.393 --> 1:04:06.060
ARE YOU OKAY?

1:04:06.062 --> 1:04:07.828
CLAIRE, ARE YOU OKAY?

1:04:09.230 --> 1:04:12.232
YEAH, I'M OKAY.

1:04:12.234 --> 1:04:13.266
ARE YOU GUYS?

1:04:13.268 --> 1:04:14.533
YEAH.
YEAH.

1:04:14.535 --> 1:04:16.368
YEAH, WE'RE --

1:04:16.370 --> 1:04:17.402
WE'RE OKAY.

1:04:17.404 --> 1:04:19.404
WE'RE OKAY.

1:04:38.486 --> 1:04:40.320
OHH.

1:04:42.289 --> 1:04:45.057
OH, THEY HAVE
EVERYTHING HERE.

1:04:53.966 --> 1:04:55.967
LOOK AT ALL THIS FOOD.

1:05:02.340 --> 1:05:04.541
HEY, ZOE.

1:05:06.944 --> 1:05:08.844
LOOK AT ALL THIS.

1:05:10.847 --> 1:05:12.246
HUH?

1:05:15.617 --> 1:05:17.618
THERE'S...

1:05:17.620 --> 1:05:19.886
THERE'S BOOKS AND GAMES AND...

1:05:19.888 --> 1:05:21.053
HEY, DAD?

1:05:21.055 --> 1:05:22.220
...MORE TOYS, THAT --

1:05:22.222 --> 1:05:23.621
YE -- YEAH?

1:05:25.991 --> 1:05:28.191
HOW LONG
DO WE HAVE TO STAY HERE?

1:05:31.161 --> 1:05:35.030
I -- I DON'T KNOW.

1:05:35.032 --> 1:05:38.533
NOT --
HOPEFULLY NOT VERY LONG.

1:05:38.535 --> 1:05:41.302
W-WE JUST GOT TO WAIT
TILL THEY CLEAR THIS UP.

1:05:41.304 --> 1:05:42.603
AND THEN...

1:05:44.539 --> 1:05:46.606
HONEY, W--

1:05:46.608 --> 1:05:50.176
WHAT HAPPENED UP THERE
WAS A MISTAKE.

1:05:50.178 --> 1:05:54.647
IT'S A TERRIBLE,
T-TERRIBLE MISTAKE.

1:05:54.649 --> 1:05:57.049
IT WASN'T A MISTAKE.

1:06:01.420 --> 1:06:03.654
THE SHELTER DOOR CUT ME.

1:06:05.391 --> 1:06:08.392
THE VIRUS
MUST HAVE GONE AIRBORNE.

1:06:08.394 --> 1:06:10.193
WE'RE INFECTED.

1:06:27.241 --> 1:06:28.574
PLEASE, JUST LET US GO.

1:06:28.576 --> 1:06:30.542
NO!
JUST LET US GO.

1:06:30.544 --> 1:06:32.277
YOU COOPERATE,
ANSWER MY QUESTIONS,

1:06:32.279 --> 1:06:34.245
I'LL DO WHAT I CAN
TO HELP YOU AND YOUR DAUGHTER.

1:06:34.247 --> 1:06:35.279
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

1:06:35.281 --> 1:06:37.381
YES, YES.

1:06:37.383 --> 1:06:39.583
THAT SHELTER WE FOUND YOU IN.
HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN THERE?

1:06:39.585 --> 1:06:41.284
SINCE THE BEGINNING.

1:06:41.286 --> 1:06:43.152
DID YOU EVER COME INTO CONTACT
WITH ANYONE ELSE?

1:06:43.154 --> 1:06:44.486
FAMILY? NEIGHBORS?
IT WAS ONLY US.

1:06:44.488 --> 1:06:47.121
DAD SAYS
WE'RE THE ONLY ONES LEFT.

1:06:48.189 --> 1:06:49.956
"ZOE."

1:06:49.958 --> 1:06:54.359
I HAVE A LITTLE GIRL
ABOUT YOUR AGE.

1:06:54.361 --> 1:06:57.095
GODDAMN SHAME.

1:07:00.499 --> 1:07:02.165
NO!

1:07:02.167 --> 1:07:04.367
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
YOU SAID YOU WOULD HELP US.

1:07:04.369 --> 1:07:06.602
ON MY ORDER.
I WON'T LET YOU
TOUCH HER.

1:07:06.604 --> 1:07:08.337
I WON'T LET YOU
TOUCH HER!

1:07:08.339 --> 1:07:09.438
I WILL NOT LET YOU
TOUCH HER!

1:07:09.440 --> 1:07:10.572
I WON'T LET YOU
TOUCH HER!

1:07:10.574 --> 1:07:12.140
I WILL NOT LET YOU
TOUCH HER!

1:07:12.142 --> 1:07:13.207
I WILL NOT LET YOU
TOUCH HER!

1:07:13.209 --> 1:07:14.308
MOM, NEVER LOSE CONTROL!

1:07:14.310 --> 1:07:16.109
KEEP AWAY!
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS!

1:07:16.111 --> 1:07:17.944
KEEP AWAY, KEEP AWAY,
KEEP AWAY!

1:07:17.946 --> 1:07:19.578
REMEMBER RULE NUMBER TWO --
NEVER LOSE CONTROL.

1:07:19.580 --> 1:07:21.313
Keep away.

1:07:23.183 --> 1:07:24.615
DON'T FORGET RULE TWO,
CLAIRE.

1:07:24.617 --> 1:07:26.416
NO MATTER WHAT,
WE HAVE TO STAY UNDER CONTROL.

1:07:26.418 --> 1:07:28.117
WE HAVE TO STAY CALM.

1:07:28.119 --> 1:07:29.585
NEVER LET ANGER TAKE OVER.

1:07:29.587 --> 1:07:31.987
NO, NO, NO!

1:07:31.989 --> 1:07:33.621
THEY'RE DIFFERENT THAN WE ARE,
AND THAT MAKES THEM

1:07:33.623 --> 1:07:35.122
AS SCARED OF US
AS WE ARE OF THEM.

1:07:35.124 --> 1:07:36.723
WE'RE NOT ANIMALS.

1:07:36.725 --> 1:07:38.458
SOMETIMES
THE TRUTH'S HIDDEN FROM US.

